Plum Holding Inc said it has started itspreviously-announced offer to purchase 664,400 common shares ofHolly Sugar Corp at 95 dlrs each.    In a newspaper advertisement, the firm said the offer,proration period and withdrawal rights expire November 17unless extended. The offer, which has been approved by theHolly board and is to be followed by a merger in whichremaining shares are to be exchanged for cumulative redeemableexchangeable preferred stock, is conditioned on receipt of atleast 664,400 shares, which would give Plum a two thirdsinterest, and the receipt of financing. Reuter&#3;